locality: MOROMANGA: Andasibe, Andranomenabe, north-south ridge east of river.Ridgetop and sidesof crest, primary montane forest rich in bamboos.
Eastern outskirts of Ranomafana, along Tana to Brickaville road, 50m from road side.
Tolanaro, St Luce forest, south of road.
Maroantsetra: Masoala Peninsula, Antalavia, swampy valleybottom at c. 400 m, primary forest rich in palms and pandans
